                                                                                              PM-19           PRIVACY PROGRAM LEADERSHIP ROLE
                                                                                                              ASSESSMENT OBJECTIVE:
                                                                                                              Determine if:

                                                                                                              PM-19[01]         a senior agency oﬃcial for privacy with authority, mission, accountability, and
                                                                                                                                resources is appointed;

                                                                                                              PM-19[02]         the senior agency oﬃcial for privacy coordinates applicable privacy requirements;

                                                                                                              PM-19[03]         the senior agency oﬃcial for privacy develops applicable privacy requirements;

                                                                                                              PM-19[04]         the senior agency oﬃcial for privacy implements applicable privacy requirements;

                                                                                                              PM-19[05]         the senior agency oﬃcial for privacy manages privacy risks through the
                                                                                                                                organizaon-wide privacy program.




